data.description: Beautiful country property sitting on just under 2 wooded acres with a year-round creek bordering the entire length of the property. Live in the country and be only minutes from town. Throughout the home you will experience ample lighting, beautiful luxury vinyl plank floor, quartz and granite countertops and tile backsplash. The custom cabinets add design to this open concept chef?s kitchen with GE Monogram appliances. Enjoy large gatherings on an incredible covered back porch overlooking the creek or around the fire pit. The creek access allows you to cool down during the hot summer months and maybe even catch a crawfish. Enjoy the detached shop that comes equipped with 200-amp power. No worries about ever losing power with a generator that will kick in without you even noticing. This property includes two RV parking spaces, one with full hookups and the other with power and water hookups. Sellers took the extra step to build this wonderful home higher than normal and so this property does NOT require flood insurance! The list of features are endless, this property is definitely a must see.
